		</div>
		<div class="panel-body">
		<p>Located at Armação Beach, at the north of the island, only 7 km (4.6 miles) from the village, Armação 
		dos Ventos is your beach house at Ilhabela.</p>
		<p>In the midst of greenery, ideal for families, the relaxed atmosphere of the inn provides the interaction 
		between guests and regulars, favoring the beginning of great friendships.</p>
		<p>It has 13 comfortable suites, 10 with a view to the São Sebastião canal. It also has 10 cozy cottages
		of two bedrooms, bathroom, living room and adjoining kitchen, with an option for monthly lease.</p>
		<p>By choice, we DO NOT have TV and minibar in suites. Enjoy your days in Armacao dos Ventos to read 
		a good book, dating, chat, make new friends, play with your kids, play sports or simply doing nothing !!</p>
		<p>Armação dos Ventos offers a delicious breakfast, adult and kiddie pools, restaurant with varied 
		menu bar, satellite TV room, wireless Internet, beach service and guest parking.</p>
		<p>We also indicate the best tours and activities related to ecotourism.</p>
		<p>Come and have a good time and have fun with us. We wait for you!</p>
		<p>See some pictures <a href="http://www.bl3.com.br/armacao-dos-ventos">here</a>.</p>
